Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 38
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 33
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: From the publisher: "Yusei enters the D1 Grand Prix. There are new rivals and the competition will be fierce. Can Yusei battle his way to the top, or is he destined to crash and burn?"
Title: YU-GI-OH 5D'S, VOL. 2
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry. In this volume, the boys face some fierce competition.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 9
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 6
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 3
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: In a distant future, the government decides to ban books and the libraries have formed their own group to defend their collections. In this volume, a book burning!
Title: LIBRARY WARS: LOVE & WAR, VOL. 7
Author: Kiiro Yumi

Description: Welcome to life in Ikebukuro, a Japanese city with lots of unusual activity, including the Black Biker, who is rumored to be headless.
Title: DURARARA!!, VOL. 1
Author: Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi
Contributor: by Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi

Description: From the publisher: "Nanami is shocked to discover that the townsfolk consider her shrine abandoned." Will her work to revitalize the shrine pay off?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 7
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 8
Author: Yana Toboso
